Rent Car Application
A responsive web application designed for car rentals, built using pure JavaScript to demonstrate core proficiency in DOM manipulation, asynchronous programming, and client-side data handling without external frameworks.

🚀 Technology Stack
Language: Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)

Markup: HTML5

Styling: SCSS / CSS3

Data Fetching: Fetch API

State Persistence: LocalStorage

🛠 Key Features
Dynamic vehicle catalog with real-time category filtering.

Client-side form validation for booking requests.

Seamless UI updates using native DOM manipulation.

Fully responsive design optimized for desktop and mobile devices.

📦 Getting Started
Clone the repository:
git clone [your-repository-link]

Navigate to the project directory:
cd rent-car-project

Open the project:
Simply open index.html in your browser or use a Live Server extension.

